{"tid":658741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就黎被人逼到無家可歸","createTime":"2018-05-09T08:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T09:53:29.000Z","uid":173573,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5128db0ce6df748f7c40ad55b538b1e0245bddcd","tid":658741,"uid":173573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"我七八歲開始就同姑姐一家住。<br />\n<br />\n姑姐同表哥都對我超級好。幾年前姑姐就搬走左。同一時間，姑姐另外一個仔同佢老婆搬左翻黎住。表哥两公婆一直都唔鐘意我住係到，不過佢呀媽又比我住，所以佢無辦法趕我走。於是我同佢两公婆，佢家姐就一齊住。<br />\n<br />\n依排佢两公婆就岀招想我自動話要搬，唔想做醜人。佢地嘅招數包括罷曬啲衣櫃，唔比我用。擺啲雜物入我間房，係間房到做公司野，唔比我訓覺，家用買嗰啲野食講到明我唔食得，要食自己買。得閒用佢把賤嘴話我幾句。但係一直都冇岀到聲趕我走。尋日佢趁屋企冇人，就同我講你唔鐘意咪唔好係到住囉，依到係&rdquo;我&rdquo;屋企呀。跟住我就當聽唔到走左入房。<br />\n<br />\n嗰一刻又好想搬，不過我一搬又正中佢地下懷。加上人工超低。所以得個唸字。<br />\n<br />\n條仆街同佢老婆人工加埋起碼十萬，手揸幾層樓，食住屋企，又唔洗交家用。我唸佢同佢老婆唯一睇唔順眼就係我。<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦，我究竟應該繼續抗戰定係投降，認輸走人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  繼續住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搬"},{"pid":"cac7b02146de43b3c31bf66a4e8e9baf115e79ef","tid":658741,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:51:05.000Z","msg":"搬黎同我住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4e901645ede6187e6b9911688d4cbafae1bf32","tid":658741,"uid":172825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:53:39.000Z","msg":"唔好搬呀，最多啲洗費你自己畀返<br />\n你可以同佢講我明白㗎啦多謝你提點(要微笑)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後一直住落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9666fe73c2e3d6793136b20bf9bdbc69253dfd7","tid":658741,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:33:02.000Z","msg":"你姑姐唔幫你你可以點？"},{"pid":"bbb9aa3a440cd1f155b3fe7c88ea8f5fecc431fb","tid":658741,"uid":173573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9666fe73c2e3d6793136b20bf9bdbc69253dfd7","tid":658741,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:33:02.000Z","msg":"你姑姐唔幫你你可以點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"姑姐唔知"},{"pid":"3ec92cd794366daf67f1b74bdc13cbf9f859c60f","tid":658741,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbb9aa3a440cd1f155b3fe7c88ea8f5fecc431fb","tid":658741,"uid":173573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9666fe73c2e3d6793136b20bf9bdbc69253dfd7","tid":658741,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:33:02.000Z","msg":"你姑姐唔幫你你可以點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"姑姐唔知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁你醒 d 俾佢知啦"},{"pid":"d9b49af283e485cd6bc24296ef55645937c73b73","tid":658741,"uid":173573,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3ec92cd794366daf67f1b74bdc13cbf9f859c60f","tid":658741,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbb9aa3a440cd1f155b3fe7c88ea8f5fecc431fb","tid":658741,"uid":173573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9666fe73c2e3d6793136b20bf9bdbc69253dfd7","tid":658741,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:33:02.000Z","msg":"你姑姐唔幫你你可以點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"姑姐唔知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁你醒 d 俾佢知啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:49:16.000Z","msg":"一個係佢個仔，一個吾係。知又點。<br />\n等多一两年佢两公婆生仔佢地可能就搬"},{"pid":"15ff8e554fd8b83390cb5aca4377890ce85e8b08","tid":658741,"uid":175112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:49:54.000Z","msg":"寄人籬下 <br />\n你冇為自己打算架咩 唔通真係諗住住成世"},{"pid":"5ab68c4f1bd13b8ad4b3522c9a6c4a7676b91a5e","tid":658741,"uid":173573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15ff8e554fd8b83390cb5aca4377890ce85e8b08","tid":658741,"uid":175112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:49:54.000Z","msg":"寄人籬下 <br />\n你冇為自己打算架咩 唔通真係諗住住成世"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"有，所以唔想岀去住，因為洗費會大好多，更加儲唔到錢"},{"pid":"d204967a23d187485d0940ac9769884c64dc8286","tid":658741,"uid":11540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母大陸狗就咪撚留係到啦"}]}